'''''Mabata Bata''''', ni filime yerekana ikinamico ya Mozambike yo muri 2017 iyobowe na Sol de Carvalho ikaba yarayikoranye hamwe na Rodrigo Areias na Ricardo Freitas kuri Bando à parte Promarte Films.  Filime yakuwe mu nkuru ngufi “The Day Mabata Bata Exploded” yanditswe n'umwanditsi wa [[Mozambike]] Mia Couto.   Filime isobanura ubuzima bwa Azariya, umwungeri ukiri muto wimfubyi wita ku bushyo bwinka. Nubwo arota kujya mwishuri, nyuma aherekejwe na Mabata Bata, impfizi nini yubushyo kugirango akomeze ubuzima bwe. 

Amashusho ya firime ya TV yasohotse ku ya 30 Mata 2017 muri [[Porutugali]] na 1 Gicurasi 2017 muri [[Berezile]]. Ku ya 30 Mutarama 2019, iyi filime yasohotse mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam mu [[Buholandi]]. Filime yafatiwe hirya no hino muri Chibuto, Gaza na Mozambique. 

